    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269490/extras/4e1890c59ff121d2d453b4dc006fdf52.avif?t=1765297996\" width=595 height=429 /></span><br><i>· ⌒ ✧ ･ﾟ * ♱ ✮ · R A W R · ✮ ♱ * ･ﾟ✧ ⌒ ·</i><br><br>Small Town Emo is a romantic GAMEBOY walking simulator with a healthy dollop of mid-2000's awkwardness! Take control of main character Ken, and guide him through a series of small town New Zealand locations rendered in pixelated GameBoy-style graphics. <br><br>Talk to characters, solve simple puzzles, make (occasional) dialogue choices, and explore! Navigate through the complexities of a teenage crush, and let the story of this small town emo kid unfold around you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269490/extras/26ac115372e6b5d873ff656f4bf8db7f.poster.avif?t=1765297996\" width=292 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269490/extras/26ac115372e6b5d873ff656f4bf8db7f.webm?t=1765297996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269490/extras/26ac115372e6b5d873ff656f4bf8db7f.mp4?t=1765297996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269490/extras/d2364c0d6f13fafec6d9d12a5cb4a956.poster.avif?t=1765297996\" width=292 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269490/extras/d2364c0d6f13fafec6d9d12a5cb4a956.webm?t=1765297996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269490/extras/d2364c0d6f13fafec6d9d12a5cb4a956.mp4?t=1765297996\" type=\"video/mp4\">